data.description: Home will be open throughout the Parade of Homes 2/16/2024-2/26/2024 12:00 pm -5:00 pm daily, including Sundays. Welcome to your dream home! Experience tranquility and embrace the utmost privacy in this stunning residence. Situated on a spacious lot, the property offers breathtaking views that will leave you in awe. Step inside and be captivated by the open floor plan, specifically designed for seamless entertainment and hosting memorable gatherings. Indulge in the luxury of indoor-outdoor living, where you can seamlessly move between the interior and multiple outdoor spaces, including two expansive patios perfect for soaking up the sun or enjoying a cozy evening beside the fire pit. Immerse yourself in relaxation with your very own hot tub, providing a private sanctuary to unwind and rejuvenate. The property also boasts an oversized garage, providing ample space for all your vehicles and storage needs. And let's not forget about the environmentally-friendly features such as solar panels, ensuring both sustainability and savings. To add a touch of serenity, the home also includes enchanting water features that create a peaceful ambiance. Don't miss this incredible opportunity to own a truly exceptional home that embodies everything you've been searching for!
